    <span class="eyebrow">Updated April 2026</span>
  </div>
  <ul class="now-list">
    <li>Building Cardboard Critters — the cardboard material pipeline is mostly dialed in; the critter AI behavior tree is what's currently on the wall.</li>
    <li>Filming a State Trees series for the channel.</li>
    <li>Studying for the Unreal Authorized Instructor certification.</li>
    <li>Reading slowly through a stack of design and architecture books, mostly at the kitchen table.</li>
